title: Trevor Interviews Jennifer Garner About Her Save with Stories Initiative
itunes:title: Trevor Interviews Jennifer Garner About Her Save with Stories Initiative
description:
Trevor enlists his correspondents to help him figure out how to make a protective mask, and actress Jennifer Garner discusses her charitable initiative, Save with Stories.
